@NODE README "iTidy v2.0"
@{b}@{u}iTidy v2.0@{uu}@{ub}

@{b}A Workbench Icon & Window Tidy Tool for AmigaOS 3.x@{ub}

@{b}Table of Contents@{ub}

1. 
2. 
